mouse or arrow keys - look
WASD                - move
Shift               - run
Space               - jump
Ctrl                - crouch (toggle)
Alt                 - freelook - turn head only, not the whole body (toggle)
p                   - step over small obstacles, e.g. walk up the stairs (toggle)
m                   - 1st/3rd person camera (toggle)
i                   - reincarnate/suicide

right click         - use
wheel down          - take to inventory
middle click        - grab/drop
wheel up            - throw (when holding an object)

F11                 - screenshot (saved to ~/.openzone/screenshot-DATE.jpg)
F12                 - minimize and freeze
